      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. It is honestly in such incredible shape, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I have taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection inside and out. I'm honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know it is going to make its next owner so happy. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take a look!",
