      "description": "Presenting an absolute jewel for the serious enthusiast: a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives as though it just left the showroom floor. The exterior is finished in a flawless deep gloss, free of even the smallest stone chips or swirl marks, and has been treated with a multi-layer ceramic coating for lasting protection. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of perfection; the premium leather seats remain supple with no bolster wear, and every surface, from the hand-stitched dashboard to the polished trim, is immaculate. All technological features and driver-assist systems function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in peak condition, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule and climate-controlled storage. With exceptionally low mileage and a complete service dossier, this is a rare opportunity to own a preserved example of automotive excellence that satisfies the most demanding standards.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
